  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447600/extras/9e5063cba4949e81361df373768dae6f.poster.avif?t=1652022306\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447600/extras/9e5063cba4949e81361df373768dae6f.webm?t=1652022306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447600/extras/9e5063cba4949e81361df373768dae6f.mp4?t=1652022306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Pandemos is an Arcade-Defender style game with simplified controls where we must destroy all the Agent Viruses in every point of the world and save the Cells from Extinction.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><strong>Eliminate all Agents before they attack the Cells, making them new Agents:</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447600/extras/c2105875b40d22a20170437f87468062.poster.avif?t=1652022306\" width=600 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447600/extras/c2105875b40d22a20170437f87468062.webm?t=1652022306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447600/extras/c2105875b40d22a20170437f87468062.mp4?t=1652022306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Use the specials of each protector to defend the Cells:</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447600/extras/430869545cb129c2bc4159040b7f9273.poster.avif?t=1652022306\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447600/extras/430869545cb129c2bc4159040b7f9273.webm?t=1652022306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447600/extras/430869545cb129c2bc4159040b7f9273.mp4?t=1652022306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Twelve different enemy types scattered in each stage:</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447600/extras/688d73be511b367c463eb907dbf3a5bf.avif?t=1652022306\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><br><strong>Five different protectors with specific skills and specials:</strong><br><i>-I unlocked the guards accumulating points when completing the levels.</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447600/extras/7ca26d82d5a333bfb8f9085d670490c7.poster.avif?t=1652022306\" width=600 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447600/extras/7ca26d82d5a333bfb8f9085d670490c7.webm?t=1652022306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447600/extras/7ca26d82d5a333bfb8f9085d670490c7.mp4?t=1652022306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>And much more:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Several stages at different points in the world of Pandemos<br></li><li> Beware of the Hordes of Virus Agents<br></li><li> Simplified gameplay<br></li><li> Recommended for fans of Pixelart-style games<br></li><li> Soundtrack with fun and carefully selected mood<br></li><li> Designed for players who enjoy fun Arcade-style games, differentiated Tower Defense<br></li><li> Game inspired by the current moment of Pandemic</li></ul><br>Will you be able to control the dangerous threats in Pandemos, through the Protectors and their abilities and prevent the complete extinction of the Cells?",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447600/extras/9e5063cba4949e81361df373768dae6f.poster.avif?t=1652022306\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447600/extras/9e5063cba4949e81361df373768dae6f.webm?t=1652022306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447600/extras/9e5063cba4949e81361df373768dae6f.mp4?t=1652022306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Pandemos is an Arcade-Defender style game with simplified controls where we must destroy all the Agent Viruses in every point of the world and save the Cells from Extinction.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><strong>Eliminate all Agents before they attack the Cells, making them new Agents:</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447600/extras/c2105875b40d22a20170437f87468062.poster.avif?t=1652022306\" width=600 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447600/extras/c2105875b40d22a20170437f87468062.webm?t=1652022306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447600/extras/c2105875b40d22a20170437f87468062.mp4?t=1652022306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Use the specials of each protector to defend the Cells:</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447600/extras/430869545cb129c2bc4159040b7f9273.poster.avif?t=1652022306\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447600/extras/430869545cb129c2bc4159040b7f9273.webm?t=1652022306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447600/extras/430869545cb129c2bc4159040b7f9273.mp4?t=1652022306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Twelve different enemy types scattered in each stage:</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447600/extras/688d73be511b367c463eb907dbf3a5bf.avif?t=1652022306\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><br><strong>Five different protectors with specific skills and specials:</strong><br><i>-I unlocked the guards accumulating points when completing the levels.</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447600/extras/7ca26d82d5a333bfb8f9085d670490c7.poster.avif?t=1652022306\" width=600 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447600/extras/7ca26d82d5a333bfb8f9085d670490c7.webm?t=1652022306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447600/extras/7ca26d82d5a333bfb8f9085d670490c7.mp4?t=1652022306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>And much more:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Several stages at different points in the world of Pandemos<br></li><li> Beware of the Hordes of Virus Agents<br></li><li> Simplified gameplay<br></li><li> Recommended for fans of Pixelart-style games<br></li><li> Soundtrack with fun and carefully selected mood<br></li><li> Designed for players who enjoy fun Arcade-style games, differentiated Tower Defense<br></li><li> Game inspired by the current moment of Pandemic</li></ul><br>Will you be able to control the dangerous threats in Pandemos, through the Protectors and their abilities and prevent the complete extinction of the Cells?",
